### GET homepage
GET http://localhost:8080/
Accept: text/html

### GET available slots
GET http://localhost:8080/slots
Accept: text/html

### GET all appointments
GET http://localhost:8080/appointments
Accept: text/html

### GET booking form
GET http://localhost:8080/book
Accept: text/html

### POST book slot 1 as user 2
POST http://localhost:8080/book
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

slotId=1&userId=2

### POST cancel appointment 1
POST http://localhost:8080/appointments/1/cancel
Accept: text/html

### POST send notification for appointment 1
POST http://localhost:8080/appointments/1/notify
Accept: text/html

### POST directly to mock notification service
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentId": 1,
  "recipientEmail": "tester@studio.com",
  "recipientName": "Vincent Do",
  "serviceName": "Game QA Testing: Optimization Tests",
  "slotTime": "2026-01-01 12:00 - 2026-06-01 12:00",
  "messageType": "BOOKING_CONFIRMATION"
}

### GET health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: application/json
